			<p class="infopara">Our portal boasts an intuitive design that makes navigation and interaction a breeze.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="info-box">
			<i class="fa-solid fa-bell custom-icon"></i>
			<h3>Appointment Reminders</h3>
			<p class="infopara">Stay on top of your healthcare schedule with timely appointment reminders sent directly to your registered email or mobile number.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="info-box">
			<i class="fa-solid fa-phone-volume custom-icon"></i>
			<h3>24/7 Accessibility</h3>
